Our Purpose

We aim to increase the quality of education.

We are convinced the lack of quality education is as a result of inacessibility to financial funds. As such we have built a technological solution to make affordable finance available to all.

Akuna matata

No worries about paying school fee in lump-sum

Cost of education in Nigeria can be high. We understand the pressure during school fees seasons and the termly payment doesn’t suit how you earn. Let help’s pay the school fee while you pay back weekly or monthly.
